<p>â€œFirst, go to FÃ¨nn and ï¬nd out more. They donâ€™t say when the grave has to be moved. Itâ€™s supposedly urgent but the tone is about as dry as a shipping report. Urgent in this country could mean tomorrow or ten years from now.â€</p>
